our professionals also have an in depth knowledge of swaps and other derivative produces enabling them to fully achieve our clients’ financing goals and objectives… visit page financial advisory stern brothers serves as financial advisor for a number of local governments agencies and institutions in connection with their bond offerings and other financial needs stern brothers’ investment bankers work collaboratively with our clients to identify the most advantageous financial strategies and professionally execute them on their behalf… visit page project finance the stern brothers’ investment bankers provide longterm financing solutions to corporations municipalities private companies and nonprofit organizations located through the country regarding infrastructure and industrial projects based upon the projected cash flows of the project rather than the balance sheets of the borrower… visit page remarketing stern brothers currently serves as remarketing agent for almost  billion of short term variablerate taxable and taxexempt bonds and notes for projects throughout the united states and is ranked ninth nationally based upon the number of transactions remarketed during the past three years the firm’s remarketing portfolio has grown by more than  billion the firm has been underwriting and remarketing vrdns since  and has developed a reputation within the vrdn market for creating efficient costeffective and seamless transactions… visit page sales  trading the stern brothers’ sales team consist of proven professionals with established buyside client relationships which allows stern brothers to leverage off its longterm commitment to public finance and provides insight into the prevailing buying  trading market trends… visit page underwriting stern brothers has raised billions of dollars to finance our clients’ projects by acting as the underwriter for their bond and debt offerings in recommending the method for structuring and selling bonds we are focused solely on identifying the best financing options available for the client in addition to public offerings stern brothers has the ability to privately place debt in situations where the borrower is unable to issue investment grade rated bonds whether through a private placement or a public offering stern brothers bankers have the longterm relationships and market knowledge to achieve the best financing execution for our clients… visit page due to limitations placed on all broker dealers by the sec and msrb stern brothers is unable to serve as both financial advisor and underwriter on the same transaction     stern brothers  co stern brothers a woman owned investment bank show menu our firm stern brothers  co is an independent womanowned business enterprise wbe investment bank we work with clients in specific market sectors providing knowledge and experience and thereby ensuring the most effective financing transactions specializing in structuring unique solutions for clients we have served thousands of municipal issuers and corporations in our history our team is eager to work with you in the structuring analyzing underwriting sales and distribution of your debt obligations peggy “pepe” finn chairman  ceo company history morris and sigmund stern immigrated to the united states from germany at the end of the th century because their bavarian village was too small to contain their dreams for a better life even as teenagers the brothers knew that people who succeed in business create their own opportunities learn more who we are stern brothers is a wholly womanowned business and is one of the few remaining independent private investment banks in the country as a privatelyheld investment bank stern brothers is not tied to larger brokerdealers or commercial banks that may have priorities other than public finance or that may have excessive exposure to derivatives or credit default swaps in addition unlike our competitors the majority of the capital of our firm is dedicated to public finance learn more community partner stern brothers is headquartered in st louis mo and has offices across the country our staff is committed to the communities we serve and are proud to be partners with many organizations learn more offices st louis headquarters  maryland ave suite  st louis mo    atlanta  woodfare lane nw kennesaw ga    chicago  west erie street suite  chicago il   cleveland  crocker park blvd suite  westlake oh    denver  east th avenue denver co    houston  woodway suite  houston tx    kansas city  west th street suite  kansas city mo    los angeles  ventura blvd suite  sherman oaks ca    new jersey  bay avenue point pleasant beach nj     new york  park avenue  new york ny    new york  colonial drive huntington ny     new york  palermo street hollis ny     ohio  crocker park blvd suite  westlake oh     industry memberships want to join our team the success of stern brothers  co is reflective of the team of qualified and experienced staff who exemplify integrity and professionalism submit your resume stern brothers  co home  stern brothers  co show menu stern brothers  co is the nation’s largest certified  womanowned business enterprise “wbe” investment bank as one of the few remaining independent private investment banks in the country we provide successful underwriting private placement financial advisory credit enhancement and remarketing services for our clients across the country stern brothers operates on a national scope with  offices across the country our bankers are seasoned highly experienced professionals each of whom has had many years of investment banking experience prior to being recruited by stern brothers it is a depth and breadth of knowledge garnered from years of working in public finance it is easy for us to take the long term view stern brothers has been in investment banking since  we are a family business privately held and dedicated not to wall street or a bank holding company but to our clients the governmental entities a