ll be able to pull more accurate and robust data to be used for client pitchesadvice to managementthe lack of strategic vision creates a chaotic approach to the day to day business high turnover and more roadblocks than necessary for future growth find a focus in public finance and become the market leader in that space  wasting time and resources to chase everything ensures that nothing happens there is an opportunity with the firms platform for a lot of growth but the current mgmt is not able to capitalize on it the firm is a prime example of a small business that has a lot of potential to unlock value but is unable to due so because of the inabilities and resistance from its owneroperator finding a competent leadership team with the experience desire and ambition to revamp the firms platform is needed more each day until then expect the firm to continue to experience high turnover infighting between its lead bankers inability to compete on par with other public finance firms stunted growth ruined relationships and most disastrous failure to best serve current and future clientsshare on facebookshare on twittershare on whatsappshare via emailcopy linklink copiedflag as inappropriateflag as inappropriatehelpful  stern brothers  co response seconds agoedit • delete stern brothers  co   pdtreviews  stern brothers  co rss feedembedcloseoutline of two peoples headswork in hr or marketinggrow your employer brandget a free employer accountcloseoutline of two peoples headswork in hr or marketinggrow your employer brandget a free employer accountcompanies to explore company benefitsdoctors valisethere are currently no benefit reviews for this companyadd benefits review job seekers also viewedpnc financial services group reviewsstarstarstarstarstar  reviewsthe blackstone group reviewsstarstarstarstarstar  reviewsedward jones reviewsstarstarstarstarstar  reviewsbny mellon reviewsstarstarstarstarstar  reviews related job searchanalyst jobsanalyst salaries kvice president jobs